OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBright
OL,6,Fand warm on Friday, chance of showers
OL,7,Fin north. Saturday cloudy and cooler,
OL,8,Fthen becoming bright with some
OL,9,Fsunshine on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
